import React from 'react'
import { Switch } from 'react-router-dom'
import Layout from './components/Layout'
import OnlyPublicRoute from './routes/OnlyPublicRoute'
import PrivateRoute from './routes/PrivateRoute'
import HomePage from './pages/HomePage'
import AziendaPage from './pages/AziendaPage'
import ProduzionePage from './pages/ProduzionePage'
import ProdottiPage from './pages/ProdottiPage'
import ContattiPage from './pages/ContattiPage'
import LoginPage from './pages/admin/LoginPage'
import DashboardPage from './pages/admin/DashboardPage'

const ApplicationRouter = () => {
  return (
    <Switch>
      <OnlyPublicRoute exact path='/' component={HomePage} layout={Layout} />
      <OnlyPublicRoute exact path='/azienda' component={AziendaPage} layout={Layout} />
      <OnlyPublicRoute exact path='/produzione' component={ProduzionePage} layout={Layout} />
      <OnlyPublicRoute exact path='/prodotti' component={ProdottiPage} layout={Layout} />
      <OnlyPublicRoute exact path='/contatti' component={ContattiPage} layout={Layout} />
      <OnlyPublicRoute exact path='/admin/login' component={LoginPage} layout={Layout} />
      <PrivateRoute exact path='/admin/dashboard' component={DashboardPage} layout={Layout} />
    </Switch>
  )
}

export default ApplicationRouter
